creator: Seamless Mobile Health Inc.
descriptionHtml: SeamlessMD is an application designed with your healthcare provider. Our program is a step-by-step guide on how to take care of yourself before and after your procedure. You will get daily real-time health reminders. Use the to-do list to prepare for your procedure. Visit the Library to explore health topics. After your procedure, answer a few health questions in the daily Health Check. Based on your answers, we will give you custom advice on how to take care of yourself. Good luck on your health journey!
descriptionShort: Track your health and get recommendations for your procedure.
